Interface PtTlsMessageValueSaslResultBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TransmissionObjectBuilder<TransportMessageValue>, TransportMessageValueBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PtTlsMessageValueSaslResultBuilderIetf

    public interface PtTlsMessageValueSaslResultBuilder
extends TransportMessageValueBuilder
    Generic builder to build a transport SASL result message value compliant to RFC 6876. It can be used in a fluent way.
